data.title: Two Door Cinema Club is Coming To El Paso, Texas in the Fall
data.meta_description: Get all the details on Two Door Cinema Club's return to El Paso for this year.
data.text:
It's been over half a decade since the indie pop rock group, Two Door Cinema Club, has been played El Paso, Texas. For years we've been waiting patiently for their return. Now we know WHEN & WHERE they are arriving back to the Sun City in 2024.

When is Two Door Cinema Club coming back to play in El Paso?

The band announced an additional 24 US dates for their 2024 North American tour. The band already had 3 Texas dates for 2024:

Tuesday May 28 at the Southside Ballroom in Dallas, TX

Wednesday, May 29th in Houston, TX at the White Oak Music Hall

and Thursday, May 20th in Austin, TX at Stubb Waller's Creek Amphitheater.

Now El Paso can be added to that list of Texas dates for TDCC.

Wednesday, September 25th at the Plaza Theater Performing Arts Center. Petey will be the special guest performing before Two Door Cinema Club in El Paso.

and additional Austin date was added for Thursday, September 26th at the Moody Amphitheater

The last time El Paso saw Two Door Cinema Club was at a venue that's sadly no longer around

September 20, 2017 was the first time we saw them perform; at the iconic Tricky Falls that's sadly closed down its doors a while ago. For anyone who wasn't lucky enough to go to that show (like me), thankfully there are videos from that performance that we can watch on YouTube. Something to hold us over until we can experience that again in the Fall.
